  <brief_title>Effect of Omacor on Triglycerides in HIV Infected Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group, Multi-Center Study to Investigate the Effect of Omacor (n-3 PUFA) on Lipid Parameters in HIV Infected Subjects Treated With HAART</official_title>
  <sponsors>
